CFB Recruiting Information - Position Groups

cfb_position_recruiting.Rd

If only start_year is provided, function will get cfb recruiting information based on position groups during that year for all FBS teams.

cfb_position_recruiting(
  start_year = NULL,
  end_year = NULL,
  team = NULL,
  conference = NULL
)

Arguments

start_year

Year (*Integer*, 4 digits YYYY, optional)
end_year

End of time period - 2020 is max value currently (*Integer* 4 digits YYYY, optional)
team

Team information (*String* optional)
conference

Conference to filter on, abbreviated (*String* optional)
